<p>
<b>SharedTree Mobile</b>
<br/>
Welcome to SharedTree! The Internet's first completely FREE, completely online family history and genealogy application.
<br/>
SharedTree is revolutionizing the genealogy industry and the way historians record and share their work by adhering to strict opensource and opencontent principles.
<br/>
Stop working in isolation and starting sharing with close and distant family members.
</p>
